{"tid":2196184,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方就721襲擊事件拘捕白衣人 警惡懲奸","createTime":"2020-09-09T16:33:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T16:39:15.000Z","uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b19061376e5bc148cee2cee7b3112ecff2eeb5e7","tid":2196184,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T16:33:43.000Z","msg":"去年元朗721襲擊事件，警方再拘捕一名男子。<br />\n<br />\n被捕的男子33歲，在葵青被警方拘捕，涉嫌參與暴動及串謀有意圖而傷人，正被扣留調查。消息指，被捕者是「白衣人」。<br />\n<br />\n警方就721襲擊事件至今共拘捕61人，當中包括47名白衣人以及14名其他人士，包括民主黨立法會議員林卓廷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=404973\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D404973&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGE7tp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=3b167ba0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D404973&h=6e9483f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=404973</a>"},{"pid":"7abd6f783623dfbb2689b9b950c58308734c9bcb","tid":2196184,"uid":334957,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T16:39:15.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n冚家剷 5 毛 PR"}]}